    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and<strong> </strong>a knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once melted, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong> and <strong>sliced leek</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 5-6 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 2,
