    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add 3/4 of the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) with your <strong>orzo </strong>and cook for 1 min, stirring to coat the grains in the oil</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
