    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and 450ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[675ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[900ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> to the pan with your orzo and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until cooked through</p><p>Tip: Stir the orzo occasionally to stop it from sticking</p>",
