    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the orzo is cooking, reboil a kettle</p><p>Wash your <strong>kale </strong>and <strong>spinach</strong>, then add them to a pot with <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 2-3 min or until wilted, once done, drain and rinse under <strong>cold running water</strong> until cool</p><p>Once cool, squeeze out as much water as you can – this is your <strong>cooked kale & spinach</strong></p>",
